settings.faq-content:
All orders are shipped out from our Los Angeles, California warehouse within 14 business days. 

You will receive a confirmation email once your order is placed, and additional emails once your order is shipped and delivered. 

We will reach out to you in the event your order is delayed.

To Check Order Status:

CLICK HERE

You will receive a tracking number as soon as your order ships. Please allow up to 14 business days for your order to ship.

Once you have been notified about your package's departure, please allow 48 hours for tracking information to update.

Once your order has left our facility we no longer have any contact or control over it and you will need to reach out to the courier directly for further information. 

Furthermore, if an order has been marked as delivered and you do not have possession of it, you will need to reach out to the courier directly for further information.
